Package: blueterra
Title: Process-Oriented Geomorphometry for Submerged Terrain
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Elvin", "Cordero", email = "cordero.elvin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("SeaMount Geospatial Labs", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Provides tools for deriving, organizing, summarizing, and
    visualizing terrain metrics from user-supplied bathymetric or elevation
    rasters. Supports submerged-landscape geomorphometry workflows including
    slope, aspect, rugosity, bathymetric position, curvature, depth-band
    summaries, transect extraction, and isobath-corridor summaries. The package
    is data-source agnostic and does not download bathymetric data.
